    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A single-page layout with a sticky navigation bar (Home, Services, Our Approach, Our Work, Contact) provides the most intuitive user flow for a company profile, allowing non-linear exploration. The key interaction is the 'Services' section, which uses a tabbed interface to manage the high density of service information, preventing user overwhelm. 'Our Work' features a Chart.js visualization of client distribution (the only quantitative data) linked to an interactive, filterable project list, providing concrete proof of their expertise. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: [Services: Report info (long list of services) -> Goal (Organize/Inform) -> Method (Tabbed interface) -> Interaction (Click tabs to show/hide detailed service lists) -> Justification (Manages high info density, interactive) -> Library (JS). Values: Report info (Core values list) -> Goal (Inform) -> Method (Card grid with Unicode icons) -> Interaction (Static, visual) -> Justification (Scannable, engaging) -> Library (HTML/Tailwind). Projects: Report info (Sample works table) -> Goal (Inform/Compare) -> Method (Chart.js Donut Chart + Filterable List) -> Interaction (Chart hover + JS filter buttons for list) -> Justification (Visualizes client distribution, adds interactivity to proof) -> Library (Chart.js, JS). ] -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->

